resource.chars:
Sorry 

 

Re: my vandalism ""revert"" on Shoe polish, I was multitasking (well, attempting to) as the phone rang and clicked the wrong thing.  Very dumb.  Will be more careful in the future.  Thanks for the message, if it wasn't being watched more closely or wasn't so obvious that could have been bad.
